.SH GUIDANCE
.IP \(bu 2
Use \f[CR]deps:report\f[R] when you want the shortest useful view.
.IP \(bu 2
Use \f[CR]dependency\-plan.json\f[R] when you need the detailed machine
artifact.
.IP \(bu 2
Prefer the normalized report over ad hoc interpretation of mixed tool
output.
.IP \(bu 2
Use the scenario tasks when you want the current Python and Java
maintenance patterns exercised end to end from the repository root.
